                "comment": "Listening comprehension course. Grading not really based on learning that specific skill, but on how well you already know Russian. Lose points on 7-9 hr take-home exams for grammatical mistakes or phonetically correct transcriptions w/ wrong spelling, or on &quot;pictures optional&quot; presentations for not including pictures! Arbitrary and demotivating.",
